      "writtenOn": "2026-04-20T10:01:58Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Issue #1: Missing validation before list access\nLocation: gui/gui_test/settings_menu/test_network_sub_menu.robot\n\n# Current code\n${ipv4_list}\u003d  Collect All IP Addresses On Both Interfaces  ipv4  ${channel}\nVerify SSH Connectivity  ${ipv4_list}  ${ssh_action}  169.254\n\nIssue: The code doesn\u0027t validate that ${ipv4_list} contains elements before passing it to Verify SSH Connectivity. If no IPv4 addresses are found, the FOR loop in Verify SSH Connectivity will silently skip without any indication.\n\nFix Required:\n\n${ipv4_list}\u003d  Collect All IP Addresses On Both Interfaces  ipv4  ${channel}\n${list_length}\u003d  Get Length  ${ipv4_list}\nIF  ${list_length} \u003e 0\n    Verify SSH Connectivity  ${ipv4_list}  ${ssh_action}  169.254\nELSE\n    Log  No IPv4 addresses found on channel ${channel}  level\u003dWARN\nEND\n\n\nWhy: Ensures test provides clear feedback when no IP addresses are available, making test failures easier to diagnose",
      "revId": "28a612f4c9f0c54ca903999934cddb040e784d84",
      "serverId": "adbd0a64-1f21-4d83-b585-671fe73cb6e4"
